// INSTALL AWS CLI IN UBUNTU MACHINE:
ubuntu@ansible-agent3:~$ aws configure
The program 'aws' is currently not installed. You can install it by typing:
sudo apt install awscli
ubuntu@ansible-agent3:~$ sudo apt install awscli
// FACING AN ERROR
ubuntu@ansible-agent3:~$ sudo apt-get update
ubuntu@ansible-agent3:~$ sudo apt install awscli		// WORKING PERFECTLY


